Then
\begin{align*}
AQ^2 + AR^2 + BP^2 + BR^2 + CP^2 + CQ^2 &= \frac{1}{4} AC^2 + \frac{1}{4} AB^2 + \frac{1}{4} AB^2 + \frac{1}{4} BC^2 + \frac{1}{4} BC^2 + \frac{1}{4} AC^2 \\
